Title: Meat Jekyll
Plot: The CSI's lives are on the line as they close in on the elusive Dr. Jekyll, and more than one member of the team may not live to see his capture, on part two of a two-part 10th season finale of CSI.
GuestStars: Jorja Fox, Joe Bologna, Matt Ross, Alex Carter, Lex Medlin, Marty Ingels, Jon Wellner, Alan Blumenfeld, Jack Conley, Bill Irwin
